<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Privacy Policy | LinkedInk</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/output.css" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto+Condensed:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&family=Sora:wght@100..800&family=Ubuntu:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;0,700;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,700&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet" />
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/assets/logo.svg" type="image/x-icon" />
</head>

<body class="bg-[#07050c] text-[#e3dfec] font-inter min-h-screen flex flex-col">
    <%- include('navbar') %>

        <main class="flex-grow pt-24 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-24">
            <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto p-6 md:p-10 lg:p-12 rounded-xl shadow-lg mt-5 mb-10">
                <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-10 text-center">
                    <span class="gradient-text">Privacy</span> Policy
                </h1>

                <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-300 mb-6">
                    At LinkedInk, your privacy is extremely important to us. This Privacy Policy outlines how we
                    collect, use, and protect your information when you use our services.
                </p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">1. Information We Collect</h2>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-400 space-y-2 text-lg md:text-xl">
                    <li>Personal information (name, email, etc.) you provide when using our tools.</li>
                    <li>Technical data such as browser type, device information, and usage patterns.</li>
                </ul>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-400 space-y-2 text-lg md:text-xl">
                    <li>To generate content and hashtags as per your request.</li>
                    <li>To improve user experience and enhance our services.</li>
                    <li>To ensure security and prevent misuse.</li>
                </ul>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">3. Data Protection</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg md:text-xl">
                    We use industry-standard security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access or
                    disclosure.
                </p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">4. Third-Party Services</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg md:text-xl">
                    We do not share your data with third-party advertisers. Any integrations we use are solely for
                    improving our service and performance.
                </p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">5. Your Consent</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg md:text-xl">
                    By using LinkedInk, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy.
                </p>

                <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 mt-8 italic">
                    This policy may be updated from time to time. Please review it periodically.
                </p>
            </section>
        </main>

        <%- include('footer') %>

            <script src="https://unpkg.com/flowbite@1.6.5/dist/flowbite.min.js"></script>
</body>

</html>